---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pagination:
  data: collections.tagList
  size: 1
  alias: tag
permalink: "/tags/{{ tag | tagSlug }}/index.html"
eleventyComputed:
  title: "Tags：{{ tag }} | {{ site.brand }}"
  description: "瀏覽 {{ site.brand }} 中與 {{ tag }} 相關的實操文章與教程。"
---

{% set tagPosts = collections.posts | postsByTag(tag) %}

<header class="archive-header">
  <p class="archive-date">Tags 聚合頁</p>
  <h2>Tags：{{ tag }}</h2>
  <p>這裏整理了本站和「{{ tag }}」相關的文章，方便按主題追蹤 DeepSeek 教學、工具部署和自動化實操。</p>
</header>

<div class="archive-grid">
  <div class="archive-list">
    {% for post in tagPosts %}
      <article class="archive-card">
        <span class="archive-date">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</span>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="archive-link">閱讀全文 &middot; 查看實操細節</a>
      </article>
    {% else %}
      <p>這個 Tags 暫時未收錄文章，後續自動生成內容後會同步更新。</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px;">
  <a href="/posts/">返回文章檔案庫</a>
</p>
